/* eslint-disable */ import React from 'react'; import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles'; import Container from '@material-ui/core/Container'; import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'; import Box from '@material-ui/core/Box'; import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'; import Avatar from '@material-ui/core/Avatar'; const useStyles = makeStyles((theme) => ({ textAlignment: { textAlign: 'left', }, quote: { textAlign: 'right', }, avatar: { width: theme.spacing(10), height: theme.spacing(10), marginRight: theme.spacing(3) }, })); export default function Team(props) { const classes = useStyles(); const content = { 'header': 'Our Team', 'description': '"None of us, including me, ever do great things. But we can all do small things, with great love, and together we can do something wonderful."', 'quote': ' – Mother Teresa', '01_image': '/teamAvatars/cq.jpg', '01_name': 'Yi Xuan Qi', '01_job': 'Junior Programmer', '02_image': '/teamAvatars/jerry.jpg', '02_name': 'Deyu Liu', '02_job': 'Junior Programmer', '03_image': '/teamAvatars/kevin.jpg', '03_name': 'Kehong Liu', '03_job': 'Junior Programmer', '04_image': '/teamAvatars/franky.jpg', '04_name': 'Chengzhi Fan', '04_job': 'Junior Programmer', ...props.content }; return (
{content['header']}
{content['description']}
{content['quote']} {content['01_name']} {content['01_job']} {content['02_name']} {content['02_job']} {content['03_name']} {content['03_job']} {content['04_name']} {content['04_job']}
); }
